            <p><strong>Without proper translation:</strong></p>
            <ul>
              <li>Birth certificate cannot support family visa</li>
              <li>Degree cannot verify employment</li>
              <li>Marriage certificate has no legal standing</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          
          <p>Our translators work with certificates daily. They know precise requirements for each document type.</p>

