          <p>Certificate translation demands absolute accuracy.</p>
          
          <ul class="accuracy-list">
            <li><strong>Misspelled name?</strong> Visa rejection.</li>
            <li><strong>Wrong date?</strong> Processing delays.</li>
            <li><strong>Missing stamp details?</strong> Authenticity questions.</li>
